text: Verónica Castro (born 26 June 1979) is a Spanish gymnast. She competed in six events at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1979 births Category:Living people Category:Spanish female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Spain Category:Gymnasts at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Gijón
